data.description: Cute little cottage in the middle of town...close to everything--shops, restaurants, bars & churches. Ample Street Parking too!!! Enjoy the sunsets from your front porch or just relax on the bench under the tree. Only 6 stairs and not in a flood zone! The owner says that there are wood floors under the carpet and bead board ceilings under the ceiling tiles. There is a full bath with a claw foot tub. Open floor plan, nice size bedrooms, exterior storage with washer & dryer hookups. The metal roof is approximately 10 years young. There is a fenced yard for your 4 legged friends! Easy to show... vacant on lock box. All facts/figures/measurements are approximate and are to be verified by the buyer.
